# 📅 Week 4 – Final Presentation & Internship Reflection

Week 4 concluded the internship with a **comprehensive presentation** of all findings, visualizations, and data models.  
It also included a reflective summary of lessons learned and professional growth throughout the project.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Compile all dashboards, insights, and findings into a **final report**
- Present outcomes to mentors and peers  
- Reflect on technical and soft skill development  
- Document internship experiences and future improvement areas  

---

## 🗂️ Deliverables

| File | Description |
|------|--------------|
| `Final_Presentation.pdf` | Consolidated slides for final showcase |
| `Internship_Reflection.md` | Personal reflection on skills, challenges, and achievements |
| `Portfolio_Summary.pdf` | Summary of dashboards and analytical outputs |

---

## 🏆 Key Highlights

- Delivered a complete **end-to-end data visualization solution**
- Demonstrated **data storytelling** through real-world datasets  
- Strengthened collaboration and communication in a remote data team  
- Developed an internship-ready **data portfolio** for future roles  

---

## 🧭 Reflection Summary

This internship deepened my ability to:
- Combine technical precision with creative visualization  
- Communicate insights clearly to non-technical stakeholders  
- Design reliable and scalable data processes  
- Apply critical thinking and analytics in professional contexts  

